hopobject.body: Can you put it on the scales, please? cefaclor monohydrate dosage Another store layout trick has to do with the clearance racks located in clothing stores. "Retailers push their clearance sales all the way in the back of the store – knowing full well I'm going to be tempted to buy any of the 1,001 items along the way," says finance guru J. Money of BudgetsAreSexy.com. His solution? Put your blinders on and head straight to the clearance deals.
